{"text_id":152327,"tokens":["The"," phenomenon"," of"," individuals"," being"," born"," with"," extra",","," functioning"," appendages",","," also"," known"," as"," poly","me","lia",","," is"," a"," rare"," and"," intriguing"," occurrence","."," While"," there"," is"," limited"," research"," on"," this"," topic",","," current"," scientific"," understanding"," suggests"," that"," the"," presence"," of"," additional"," limbs"," does"," not"," necessarily"," mean"," that"," unique"," brain"," regions"," are"," present"," for"," controlling"," them",".","\n\n","The"," development"," and"," control"," of"," limbs"," in"," the"," human"," body"," is"," a"," complex"," process"," that"," is"," primarily"," governed"," by"," genetic"," factors"," and"," signaling"," pathways"," during"," embryonic"," development","."," These"," pathways"," and"," genetic"," blueprints"," for"," limb"," development"," dictate"," the"," number",","," placement",","," and"," functionality"," of"," limbs"," in"," an"," individual","."," However",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," note"," that"," the"," brain","'","s"," organization"," and"," control"," of"," these"," limbs"," are"," not"," solely"," dependent"," on"," the"," number"," of"," limbs"," present",","," but"," are"," also"," influenced"," by"," other"," factors"," such"," as"," the"," individual","'","s"," experiences"," and"," interactions"," with"," the"," environment",".","\n\n","The"," human"," brain"," has"," a"," remarkable"," ability"," to"," adapt"," and"," reorgan","ize"," itself"," in"," response"," to"," changes"," in"," the"," body",","," a"," phenomenon"," known"," as"," neurop","lastic","ity","."," This"," means"," that"," if"," an"," individual"," is"," born"," with"," extra"," limbs",","," the"," brain"," may"," reorgan","ize"," itself",","," creating"," new"," neural"," connections"," and"," pathways"," to"," control"," the"," additional"," limbs",","," rather"," than"," requiring"," separate"," brain"," regions"," for"," each"," limb",".","\n\n","While"," research"," on"," individuals"," with"," poly","me","lia"," remains"," limited",","," studies"," of"," individuals"," with"," congenital"," mirror","-","hand"," syndrome"," offer"," some"," insight","."," Mirror","-","hand"," syndrome"," is"," a"," rare"," condition"," in"," which"," an"," individual"," is"," born"," with"," one"," hand"," that"," is"," underdeveloped"," or"," missing",","," and"," the"," other"," hand"," appears"," mirror","-","reversed","."," Brain"," imaging"," studies"," of"," these"," individuals"," have"," revealed"," that"," the"," brain"," regions"," responsible"," for"," hand"," movement"," are"," larger"," and"," more"," active"," in"," the"," intact"," limb",","," suggesting"," that"," the"," brain"," can"," adapt"," to"," changes"," in"," the"," body"," by"," reorgan","izing"," and"," re","dist","ributing"," existing"," neural"," resources",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," while"," the"," presence"," of"," extra"," functioning"," appendages"," may"," necessitate"," some"," reorganization"," in"," the"," brain",","," it"," is"," unlikely"," that"," unique"," brain"," regions"," are"," present"," for"," controlling"," them","."," Instead",","," the"," brain","'","s"," inherent"," plasticity"," and"," adaptability"," enable"," it"," to"," adjust"," to"," changes"," in"," the"," body"," and"," control"," additional"," limbs"," through"," reorganization"," and"," the"," creation"," of"," new"," neural"," connections"," and"," pathways","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}